import React from 'react';

class showRecord extends React.Component{
    showRecord = (Id, show, showType, theatre, seenOn, stars) => {
        this.Id = Id;
        this.show = show;
        this.showType = showType.name;
        this.theatre = theatre;
        this.seenOn = seenOn;
        this.stars = stars;
    }
};
